## Project Structure

```
src/{{namespace}}/
  Client.cs            # Main client class
  HttpClient.cs        # HTTP layer with retry logic
  OAuth2Client.cs      # OAuth 2.0 implementation
  Paginator.cs         # Async pagination
  Errors.cs            # Error class hierarchy
  Resources/           # One file per API resource
  Types/               # Data model classes
tests/                 # Unit tests (xUnit)
docs/                  # API documentation per resource
```

## Key Patterns

- All methods are async and return `Task<T>` (use `await`)
- System.Text.Json for serialization
- `IAsyncEnumerable<T>` for pagination
- PascalCase naming convention
- Path parameters are passed as method arguments
- Query parameters use optional parameter objects

